data.description: A refreshing take on open concept living, this 3-bedroom, 2-bath pool home with 2-bonus room on a spacious corner lot is a haven of comfort and style. The ample landscaping features coconut, mango and ponytail palm trees. The open floor plan is perfect for entertaining, complemented by two bonus rooms, provides flexibility in living, dining, and work areas flooded in natural light with two pocket doors extending to the pool. The heart of the home, the kitchen, features tile countertops and a large window overlooking the spacious open backyard and pool, making it easy to keep an eye on the pool area and backyard activities while cooking up delicious dishes. One of the homes features is the master bedroom, located on the ground floor with pool bath for ultimate convenience and privacy. Venturing upstairs, you'll discover the remaining two bedrooms, shared bath and 3 large hallway closets. The first of these bedrooms offers it's own private screened balcony. Stepping outside, you'll find the open pool area, a true oasis for relaxation and entertainment. Located close to Cape Elementary School, shopping, entertainment and public dock, allows for added convenience.
